      ["Why must Drawing be closed at period end?", "To reset its balance for the next accounting period."],
      ["What financial statement reflects owner’s equity?", "The balance sheet."],
      ["Why is capital identification important for FBLA exams?", "Many questions require analyzing equity effects of transactions."]
