      ["Comprehensive Income", "Total change in equity from non-owner sources during a period, includes net income and other comprehensive income."],
      ["Effect of Treasury Stock on EPS", "Repurchasing shares reduces shares outstanding, increasing EPS if net income is constant."],
      ["Example of Statement of Stockholders’ Equity", "Beginning Equity $100,000 + Net Income $20,000 – Dividends $5,000 = Ending Equity $115,000."],
      ["Example Closing Process Timeline", "Dec 31: Journalize and post closing entries; Jan 1: Begin new accounting period with only permanent accounts."]
